  <h1 class="title">UARTDriver</h1></div>
</div><!--header-->
<div class="contents">
<a name="details" id="details"></a><h2 class="groupheader">Description</h2>
<p>Serial UART Interface Driver. </p>
<p>Flexible UART driver implementation for communication with external devices. </p>
