<p>Read from the UART into a data buffer.</p>
<dl class="params"><dt>Parameters</dt><dd>
  <table class="params">
    <tbody><tr><td class="paramdir">[out]</td><td class="paramname"><code>buffer</code></td><td>The data buffer to receive into </td></tr>
    <tr><td class="paramdir">[in]</td><td class="paramname"><code>requestedLength</code></td><td>Number of bytes to read </td></tr>
    <tr><td class="paramdir">[out]</td><td class="paramname"><code>receivedLength</code></td><td>Number of bytes read </td></tr>
    <tr><td class="paramdir">[in]</td><td class="paramname"><code>blocking</code></td><td>Indicates whether to wait for requestedLength bytes to be available and read before returning, or whether to read out data currently in the buffer and return. </td></tr>
    <tr><td class="paramdir">[in]</td><td class="paramname"><code>timeout</code></td><td>Number of milliseconds to wait for data in blocking mode</td></tr>
  </tbody></table>
  </dd>
</dl>
